Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.59,Title 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.03\pos(1394,789)}"Memories Of\NSchool Days"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.47,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\pos(518,400)}South Zagan Sorcery School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That was for the school lunches! Give it back, you goddamn lowlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already paid the lunch fee, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aikawa! Help me with practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Swiped some food again? Gonna have an early lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup guys, anyone seen Risu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Risu? He went to the sorcery classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's with some bad looking guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the promised item.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you had quite the struggle this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Risu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's for the boss after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss will be pleased as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell? You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that, Aikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, the effective time of magic smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to stop hanging out with the Cross-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what those guys are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's in that bag too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use a little bit magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite going to this school I still can't put out even a milligram of smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cross-eyes are a group of people just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Scum like us can't live any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say messed up shit like that, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a rumor that the Cross-eyes have a research facility in a village called Berith, 40 km north from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the contents of that bag are going to be used for research there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss of the Cross-eyes will lead us to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You really believe in such a dreamlike story, you moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a headache again. I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,100)}Next stop: Berith...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right... He always gets those headaches and disappears somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,100)}If you wish to get off, please press the button...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,100)}And wait until the bus stops completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be impossible for me to find Aikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Berith... The Cross-eyes should have their headquarters here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the boss is there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely going to find out who killed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:26.00,Title 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,694)}"Boy Meets Girl = Battle!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm En's partner so I'm staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Stop messing around, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it! That bastard En must be controlling you with his magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill that guy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like this because of you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Can't go all out against a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never thought of you as a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your knife, Caiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong with a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Nikaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,En's enemies are my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be joking. Don't give me that bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Open... Your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Great Lord Satan, please grant my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please let Nikaido die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept this offering!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hail to the great devil king! Hail to the great devil king!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hail to the great devil king! Hail to the great devil king!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That should do the trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That bitch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman...? He's that lizard-man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, my legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido! We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said, I'm going to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido! Sto-!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, the floor collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My damn legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirror...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to kill again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to kill again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure went quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Nikaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Success! Nikaido is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hail to the great devil king!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! A devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still at the very brink of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! How should we finish her off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Strangulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not killing, I'm saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Then give me back my offering!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a deep wound... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Her contract with En!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you swear you won't tell En a word of what you just saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I do! I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All hail the great devil king! All hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Nikaido. I took out the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow it feels like I just had a long dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, Nikaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it was Caiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the one who stabbed me was someone I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Caiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was someone else... Who's still in this darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Nikaido? Where did you go? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That Nikaido... Just where did she -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. En!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That contract is a part of En's internal organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking it out should have some effect on En as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! If I put this inside my body, would that make me En's partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make a contract unless you and En exchange them using Chidaruma's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido, you have come to your senses only temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless En dies or Chidaruma releases you from the contract...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:11:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it expires during the next Blue Night it'll remain in effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Asu, how long will I be able to stay normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,En's contract has already transformed into a part of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see En again, the contract will regrow inside your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to escape somewhere far away, out of his reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, En!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, I was just feeling a bit dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Nikaido is in the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wandering around alone... She's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman and that man are not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dangerous, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody came from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking very closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the man who stabbed you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was dark so I couldn't see very well, but it wasn't Caiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? "That" is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Something evil keeps growing inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? This is a hospital dedicated to magic victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty bad, they cast a spell on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic on my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name? Where do you live? Anyone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... I can't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So memory loss as well? What a bother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He woke up just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who carried you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This has become a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got no memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well what would you like then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy still hasn't picked a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Says he doesn't like the names I come up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Names like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Scalio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you some gyoza from my place for today's visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gyoza...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've also been thinking of a name for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it's not Scalio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked through a reptile guidebook and found one that resembles you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lizard called "caiman".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about calling yourself Caiman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman... Caiman, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels nostalgic for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's close to my real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll call you Caiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman... Caiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman! Caiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a sorcerer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Risu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What did the guy in my mouth say to you, Nikaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're not the one"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For real? I don't believe you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to believe a damn sorcerer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman, listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The man in your mouth was Risu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up! There's still plenty of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee! Sque!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasukabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been sneaking out of this room while I've been away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was exploring a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been curious about this huge castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hiding you from En, don't you care about my situation at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you guys are going back to Hole tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, we're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, Nikaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her up, kid. And you too, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do, Thirteen. Our opponent's filthy rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the issue here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. We're going back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry now! There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'm also already an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The man in my mouth is Risu. If that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean the one who cast the magic on me was Risu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Risu is currently in a town called Berith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And who are you, you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know something, spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the "bastard"? Want me to throw you in hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils are super powerful and know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And who the hell are {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido! I know you're in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come out, you won't get any dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time until En gets here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She must've run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You two need to run far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Asu! But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with this liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells like mold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,En...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, h-hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just in a bad mood for a bit and ended up wrecking the church...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. As long as you're alright everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like it worked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to! Not with this liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- W-Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- As if I'd go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Asu! Please just wait a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to do something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,100)}Hey! Wait up... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,100)}Listen up, you... Hey! Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Asu! Wait...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear... If you're that worried about her wouldn't it have been better to go with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I must now go and see Chidaruma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot ignore his call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But if En find's out Nikaido is not here, he'll go looking for her immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your mask off, Chota.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha-? It c-can't be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone but her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Even the voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It took all my power to transform you into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But with this we should be able to fool En and even Chidaruma for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fucking around! Don't turn me into Nikaido on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the "bastard"? I'll throw you in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I sincerely apologize for what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm? Wait a minute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I make En hate me, I can break up his relationship with Nikaido!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good! I'm confident in my acting abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blow your cover. Don't do anything that makes you stand out. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where did the man who stabbed Nikaido disappear to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, maybe there was no such man in the first place...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps I'm overthinking this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Caiman... Just who is he, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if it was a good thing to send him away with Nikaido.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:08.30,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,298)}"Pinky Promise"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't a normal town, everything's in ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite far away from En's castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If a devil other than Asu spots us, it'll immediately get reported to En.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's going to be a bunch of devils around during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hide here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're a really amazing sorcerer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. My ability is just unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you pretending to be human in Hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost a friend... Because of my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic is very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I won't use it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran away from people like En who are aiming for my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I went to Hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I... Wanted to become a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you help me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that by fighting the sorcerers who use humans for practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I could truly become a human from Hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could become real friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any memories of my past...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And my face looks like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you don't know what kind of a human I am, are you really fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? I'm a sorcerer after all, isn't that a deal breaker...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't use magic then you're not really a sorcerer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you can promise me you won't use magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, you'll be my friend forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what the real you is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Caiman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To get my face and lost memories back...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm looking for the guy who cast this magic on me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know anything right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything's still a mystery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even mysteries will eventually be over...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I believe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What we learned from the twelfth curse:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,1. There was a mystery man in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,2. Caiman got his name from Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,3. They are friends, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything's still a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,DOROHEDORO

